<article class="bullet bullet--list" data-id="76968">
<div class="bullet__link">
<a href="/anker-powercore-magnetic-5k-wireless-review" class="bullet__image">
<figure class="image">
<img src="https://www.imore.com/sites/imore.com/files/styles/w250h188crop/public/field/image/2021/06/anker-powercore-magnetic-5k-iphone-12-pro-hero.jpg" alt="Review: Magnetically charge up on the go with Anker&#039;s PowerCore Magnetic 5K" />
</figure>
</a>
<div class="bullet__body">
<strong class="tag bullet__tag">Magnets mmkay</strong>
<h3 class="bullet__title">
<a href="/anker-powercore-magnetic-5k-wireless-review">
Review: Magnetically charge up on the go with Anker&#039;s PowerCore Magnetic 5K
</a>
</h3>
<div class="bullet__summary">
<span class="bullet__author">
Christine Chan </span>
<time class="bullet__time" datetime="2021-07-12T12:00:02-04:00">3 hours ago</time>
</div>
<p class="bullet__description">Anker is one of the leading brands when it comes to power accessories for your iPhone. If you have an iPhone 12, the PowerCore Magnetic 5K is pretty great for MagSafe wireless charging.</p>
</div>
</div>
