watchOS 8 is nothing special, but the small improvements are welcome
</a>
</h3>
<div class="bullet__summary">
<span class="bullet__author">
Luke Filipowicz </span>
<time class="bullet__time" datetime="2021-07-09T15:00:03-04:00">3 days ago</time>
</div>
<p class="bullet__description">If watchOS 8 is meant to make using the Apple Watch a more pleasant experience it has succeeded, but don't be surprised if the new software doesn't seem all that new.</p>
